  ('en', 'Expressions connues', 'In what public place could we once hear a « butterfly minute » ?', 'Coffeehouse', 'Theater', 'Museum', 'University', '3', 'Papillon was the name of a café waiter at Le Cadran in Paris: the « Minute Papillonn » told him that he could take his time.', 'https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coffeehouse'),
